WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:23.986
On today’s auspicious occasion, in a pleasant environment, such a beautiful subject – seems that many coincidences have come together.

00:00:23.986 --> 00:00:32.910
Till date nobody suggested me to speak on the subject of worship but it is so important.

00:00:32.910 --> 00:00:43.052
Especially in this land of Yoga (Yogabhumi), in our land of Bharat (India), especially in this holy land of Maharashtra,

00:00:43.052 --> 00:00:47.301
the Goddess of nature has come up with the creation of Ashtavinayakas,

00:00:47.301 --> 00:01:00.436
so what is the greatness of Ganesha, what is the importance of Ashtavinayakas etc is not known to many people.

00:01:00.436 --> 00:01:04.476
I am very surprised at this.

00:01:04.476 --> 00:01:16.446
Perhaps the people who understood everything, who knew everything –

00:01:16.446 --> 00:01:26.109
those great ascetics and saints of our holy land – they must not have been given the liberty to express,

00:01:26.109 --> 00:01:29.504
or may be nobody listened to them.

00:01:29.504 --> 00:01:38.147
Any amount of explanation about this will be inadequate and even seven lectures instead of one would be insufficient for me to speak about Shri Ganesha.

00:01:38.147 --> 00:01:45.653
Today’s auspicious day is that of ‘Ghata Pujan’.  Ghatasthapna is primordial.

00:01:45.653 --> 00:01:50.900
When this universe was created, many times.

00:01:50.900 --> 00:01:56.415
The universe has not been created only once but many times.

00:01:56.415 --> 00:02:01.097
When this universe was created, first they installed the Ghata (container).

00:02:01.097 --> 00:02:04.797
What do you mean by Ghata? One needs to understand this very deeply.

00:02:04.797 --> 00:02:12.163
Firstly, the Almighty resides in the state of Bramhatatva,(universal element or principle).

00:02:12.163 --> 00:02:19.596
We will call it entropy in English.   When there is no movement in this state,

00:02:19.596 --> 00:02:33.103
when the desire originates in this state or when the Almighty fancies desire then this desire gets established in HIM that    something new must be created in this world.

00:02:33.103 --> 00:02:36.373
Why does He get this desire? It is His desire.

00:02:36.373 --> 00:02:41.058
To understand why the Almighty has this desire is beyond the understanding of the human being.

00:02:41.058 --> 00:02:43.697
Likewise there are many things beyond the general comprehension of a human being.

00:02:43.697 --> 00:02:50.888
But as we take them for granted similarly we must accept that that God’s wish is His own hobby.

00:02:50.888 --> 00:02:54.575
It’s His desire,  He does whatever He wants to do.

00:02:54.575 --> 00:03:01.147
This desire gets merged in Him and again gets awakened.

00:03:01.147 --> 00:03:03.797
Like a person sleeps off and again awakens.

00:03:03.797 --> 00:03:10.228
After sleeping even if his desires are dormant and are with him, they get activated only when he wakes up.

00:03:10.228 --> 00:03:12.831
It is same thing with God Almighty.

00:03:12.831 --> 00:03:23.916
When He has a desire to create nature then all these waves of creation of the universe, of the desire or what we can call as waves or ripples get collected.

00:03:23.916 --> 00:03:29.464
And after accumulation, the ghat in which they get filled in – this is that ghat( container) .

00:03:29.464 --> 00:03:32.498
It is the will power of God Almighty itself.

00:03:32.498 --> 00:03:38.347
If we separate the God Almighty and his Will Power, and if we can understand it that way.

00:03:38.347 --> 00:03:40.726
It is same with us. We and our will power are different.

00:03:40.726 --> 00:03:43.776
This power takes birth first.

00:03:43.776 --> 00:03:49.534
Till the time you desire something, till then that thing and its realization does not happen.

00:03:49.534 --> 00:03:54.969
This beautiful enormous world of ours, this too is a result of somebody’s desire.

00:03:54.969 --> 00:04:05.046
Everything gets activated only after we wish it and to activate God’s desire, we need to separate it from HIM.

00:04:05.046 --> 00:04:08.367
If it remains included in the God Almighty, then it remains dormant.

00:04:08.367 --> 00:04:16.292
When it starts its work by separating from HIM, we call it as “Adishakti” .

00:04:16.292 --> 00:04:21.615
When this initial state came, then Ghatasthapana happened.

00:04:21.615 --> 00:04:25.075
This has happened many times since time immemorial.

00:04:25.075 --> 00:04:35.291
And today also when we do Ghatasthapana, we remember that eternal infinite process.

00:04:35.291 --> 00:04:40.625
Means during this time (Navratra first day) we do the Ghatasthpana. So keep in mind what a great event this is.

00:04:40.625 --> 00:04:47.551
That time what the God Almighty desired, before activating it He collected it.

00:04:47.551 --> 00:04:54.202
This was placed in a Ghat (container), the same desire today is being worshipped by us.

00:04:54.202 --> 00:04:56.226
We worshipped it today.

00:04:56.226 --> 00:05:08.293
God Almighty desired it. He made us part of humanity today. He helped us reach this great state. Hence it is our prime duty to bow to His desire.

00:05:08.293 --> 00:05:15.866
In the language of Sahaja Yoga, we call this as the desire of Mahakali or the power of Mahakali.

00:05:15.866 --> 00:05:28.345
This is the power of Mahakali and these events that take place for nine days (specially in Maharashtra) these are about the various incarnations of this Mahakali.

00:05:28.345 --> 00:05:34.439
Even today, nothing can happen before the power of Mahakali or the power of pure desire.

00:05:34.439 --> 00:05:38.723
Hence the power of pure desire is the beginning and the end also transpires in it.

00:05:38.723 --> 00:05:42.880
First of all, everything emanates from the desire and at the end it merges in it.

00:05:42.880 --> 00:05:51.275
So this power of Shri Sadashiva ( Lord Shiva), is the Adi Shakti and it moves around as Mahakali Power within us.

00:05:51.275 --> 00:06:10.156
At this juncture if we consider it as the Supreme Power, if we consider it as the formulation of the Viraat ( infinite) , the power on the left which flows through our Ida Nadi and that power is known as power of Mahakali.

00:06:10.156 --> 00:06:14.327
This is more widespread in the humans.

00:06:14.327 --> 00:06:17.896
It is not as much in the animals.

00:06:17.896 --> 00:06:24.203
This power enters us from the right side of our head.

00:06:24.203 --> 00:06:35.353
Subsequently it moves along the left side to go below the triangular bone which is the position of Lord Ganesha and ends there.

00:06:35.353 --> 00:06:44.408
Means first and foremost, the power of Mahakali gave birth only to Shri Ganesh.

00:06:44.408 --> 00:06:52.354
Then Shri Ganesha got established. Ganesh is the first deity that got established and similarly the situation of Ganesh is same as that of Mahakali.

00:06:52.354 --> 00:06:57.350
This is the seed and the whole world emanates from this seed and again gets merged with it.

00:06:57.350 --> 00:07:01.630
Similarly everything after emanating from the Ganesh element merges with Ganesh element itself.

00:07:01.630 --> 00:07:07.606
Whatever exists, Ganesh is the seed of that.

00:07:07.606 --> 00:07:12.500
Whatever appears in front of us, in action, in desire, Ganesh is the seed of it.

00:07:12.500 --> 00:07:16.704
That is why Ganesh is considered the foremost main deity.

00:07:16.704 --> 00:07:20.584
Not only that, without worshipping Shri Ganesh, we cannot do any work.

00:07:20.584 --> 00:07:28.310
Then they may be Shaiva( devotees who worship Shri Shiva), maybe Vaishnav( devotees who worship Shri Vishnu), may be devotees of Shri Bramha or anybody else – all of them first worship Shri Ganesha.

00:07:28.310 --> 00:07:34.845
The reason for this is that Shri Ganesh element was established by God Almighty as the first thing in this universe.

00:07:34.845 --> 00:07:40.783
The Ganesh principle is what we call as ‘abodhita’ or what we call as ‘innocence’ in English.

00:07:40.783 --> 00:07:44.299
This is a very subtle principle. We do not understand it.

00:07:44.299 --> 00:08:03.817
In childhood it exists in the children, everywhere we see its expression, its fragrance, wafting all over –  that is why small children are so lovable –  such  is the principle of “innocence’

00:08:03.817 --> 00:08:04.407
It is present in Shri Ganesha.

00:08:04.407 --> 00:08:11.194
It is difficult for human beings to understand this that how can one deity encompass all these things?

00:08:11.194 --> 00:08:20.238
If we look at the sun we see it has the power to give light similarly Shri Ganesha has power of ‘innocence’ .

00:08:20.238 --> 00:08:48.719
{Shree Mataji instructs in marathi}

00:08:48.719 --> 00:08:58.955
This power of ‘innocence ‘ that the God Almighty has imbibed in us , we worship this power of innocence.

00:08:58.955 --> 00:09:02.717
And we should also be such innocent beings.

00:09:02.717 --> 00:09:09.634
Many people feel that being innocent means being ignorant.

00:09:09.634 --> 00:09:19.948
The meaning behind ‘innocence’ is that just like a small child is innocent , he is naive –that naivety should come in us.

00:09:19.948 --> 00:09:23.683
We do not understand how great this principle is.

00:09:23.683 --> 00:09:28.753
Suppose a small child starts playing. Today’s kids do not have much naivety.

00:09:28.753 --> 00:09:35.422
We only are responsible  for that.  What else can we tell others.

00:09:35.422 --> 00:09:40.072
How are we following our religions. How deeply involved are we in our religions?

00:09:40.072 --> 00:09:46.530
How religious we make our children – it is dependant on that and must know this is the outcome of that.

00:09:46.530 --> 00:09:53.263
Now the presence of innocence in humans can be   identified by watching a child.

00:09:53.263 --> 00:09:57.296
A person may have it, however old he becomes, still he has that innocence.

00:09:57.296 --> 00:10:02.665
Like a small kid while playing can impersonate Shivaji, may build a fort, will do everything.

00:10:02.665 --> 00:10:04.793
Then he will leave everything and go away.

00:10:04.793 --> 00:10:07.180
One must leave everything after doing it.

00:10:07.180 --> 00:10:10.500
One must leave everything and be detached  about it.

00:10:10.500 --> 00:10:15.496
One must not get entangled in something. Must have no involvement.

00:10:15.496 --> 00:10:19.102
This is the typical behavior of children.

00:10:19.102 --> 00:10:22.120
If you give anything to any child, he will preserve it.

00:10:22.120 --> 00:10:27.777
Will preserve it for a long time. After some time he will have no feelings for it.

00:10:27.777 --> 00:10:30.870
If we take away  that thing  without letting him know, he will not feel anything about it.

00:10:30.870 --> 00:10:35.688
But there are some  things that a child may not leave which are very important to him.

00:10:35.688 --> 00:10:37.490
One of such things is his mother.

00:10:37.490 --> 00:10:41.537
He does not leave his mother. Rest any thing  of this   world you  take from him,it is alright with him –

00:10:41.537 --> 00:10:48.065
He does not understand wealth, he does not understand money, he does not understand education, he does not understand anything except his mother.

00:10:48.065 --> 00:10:54.972
This is my mother. She gave birth to me. She is everything for  me.

00:10:54.972 --> 00:10:58.677
He does not accord importance to anything other than his mother.

00:10:58.677 --> 00:11:03.194
Rabindranath Tagore has written a beautiful story.

00:11:03.194 --> 00:11:10.022
A  small child lost his way in the market place and people caught  him and asked him what he wants.’ He was continuously crying.

00:11:10.022 --> 00:11:16.551
They told him that they would give him this thing, give him horse, give him elephant. He said nothing doing , I want my mother.’

00:11:16.551 --> 00:11:21.066
And he was continuously crying for his mother.He did not eat anything offered to him.

00:11:21.066 --> 00:11:25.900
Kept on crying the whole day. He became quiet only when he met his mother.

00:11:25.900 --> 00:11:30.238
All of us have this seed element in us from the childhood itself.

00:11:30.238 --> 00:11:37.119
We do not leave our mother. We know that this mother has given birth to us.

00:11:37.119 --> 00:11:43.657
But in addition there is another mother within us that  the God almighty has given. And this mother is “Kundalini” .

00:11:43.657 --> 00:11:48.642
God almighty has curled up  Mother Kundalini and placed her in  our sacrum bone(triangular bone).

00:11:48.642 --> 00:11:51.967
She is our mother and we are continuously searching her.

00:11:51.967 --> 00:12:03.206
In all our searches whether  political, social or educational – whatever your interests may be, behind all these interests you are searching your mother.

00:12:03.206 --> 00:12:10.189
This Mother Kundalini takes you to the ultimate position where you get complete satisfaction.

00:12:10.189 --> 00:12:22.260
The search for this mother, the longing for this mother, which lies in us in a subtle form , which embraces us stays awakened due to the Ganesha principle.

00:12:22.260 --> 00:12:27.129
The person whose Ganesha element is destroyed completely he is not innocent.

00:12:27.129 --> 00:12:29.643
We observe many qualities in a person who is innocent.

00:12:29.643 --> 00:12:34.781
means he has chastity in his relations with his  mother, sister, and brother.

00:12:34.781 --> 00:12:46.703
During common interactions, social interactions, during worldly interactions God has defined one  spouse and all other people in this world –

00:12:46.703 --> 00:12:51.953
if we consider that  we have pure  relation with them as God Almighty has defined –

00:12:51.953 --> 00:12:57.498
if this is seen in your behavior  then it should be considered that the person has true innocence.

00:12:57.498 --> 00:13:03.941
This is his true attribute. The sign of innocence is that a person sees purity in all individuals.

00:13:03.941 --> 00:13:07.621
Reason is as he has purity within himself, he will not regard anyone as impure.

00:13:07.621 --> 00:13:13.649
Here we don’t have to explain about chastity as people know what chastity is.

00:13:13.649 --> 00:13:17.758
In England or America we have to explain because their minds are confused.

00:13:17.758 --> 00:13:22.269
But you all are sensible. By grace of God in this land of India

00:13:22.269 --> 00:13:29.742
say due to Ashtavinayakas or due to good deeds from your previous lives or due to the service rendered by our gurus and saints ,

00:13:29.742 --> 00:13:35.282
this is one land on this earth where holiness still prevails.

00:13:35.282 --> 00:13:40.349
It is a very great thing and you have organized the puja (worship) of this holiness.

00:13:40.349 --> 00:13:46.622
So while doing puja, you must pay attention to whether you have that holiness or not.

00:13:46.622 --> 00:13:53.693
In our Sahaja Yoga those who do not have Ganesh element they do not have the purity. He is of no use to us.

00:13:53.693 --> 00:13:59.079
We do not pay attention to such a person. But there is no way to tell upfront that you have lost this holy attribute.

00:13:59.079 --> 00:14:07.748
Even though we know all this , we cannot tell this – because this Ganapati who is installed there, he is the son of Gauri.

00:14:07.748 --> 00:14:13.870
And Gauri means the power of Kundalini  which encompasses us,  this is the power of  Gauri.

00:14:13.870 --> 00:14:19.843
Today there is Gauri Pujan(worship) and Ganesh Pujan – we must realize what a significant day it is.

00:14:19.843 --> 00:14:26.893
The Ganesh element present in us tells Gauri whether this person is alright or not.

00:14:26.893 --> 00:14:30.652
Means one must appreciate the good arrangement that is made.

00:14:30.652 --> 00:14:33.127
Means the two nadis coming from the top, Ida and Pingla…

00:14:33.127 --> 00:14:39.284
Now if you have not read about Sahaja Yoga at all then it will be a bit difficult but if you try to understand it is not that difficult.

00:14:39.284 --> 00:14:44.378
Ida and Pingala are the two nadis(channels) within us. Of these one is Mahakali and the other is Maha Saraswati. These are the two nadis.

00:14:44.378 --> 00:14:47.638
The Maha Saraswati has emanated from Maha Kali. Means she is the power of pure action.

00:14:47.638 --> 00:14:50.339
The first one is the power of pure desire and other one is the   power of pure action.

00:14:50.339 --> 00:14:57.978
Of these two powers, whatever deeds we have done in this birth as well as past births, whatever are our good deeds ,

00:14:57.978 --> 00:15:04.684
whatever are our bad deeds, this all is evaluated by Shri Ganesha who is within us.

00:15:04.684 --> 00:15:09.315
He is observing how much virtue this person has accumulated.

00:15:09.315 --> 00:15:13.321
Today’s modern people do not have any inkling about virtues and they do not even think about it.

00:15:13.321 --> 00:15:17.118
People think what sense does it make that how much virtue  one has and for what.

00:15:17.118 --> 00:15:22.257
When they don’t have any concept about virtue then sin and its atonement etc.- then knowing these things has no meaning.

00:15:22.257 --> 00:15:26.923
But the human has a feel for sin and virtue.

00:15:26.923 --> 00:15:30.221
Animals do not have this. Animals do not have feel for many things.

00:15:30.221 --> 00:15:34.889
If you walk  an animal thru dung or filth, it does not sense the smell.

00:15:34.889 --> 00:15:37.281
It does not have any appreciation for beauty.

00:15:37.281 --> 00:15:40.554
The moment you become human, you get a thought  about virtue and sin.

00:15:40.554 --> 00:15:44.199
You understand that this is wrong. This is sin, should not do this.

00:15:44.199 --> 00:15:46.017
This is a good deed, should do it.

00:15:46.017 --> 00:15:53.496
Instead of we making a judgment about sin and virtue, Shri Ganesh keeps an accurate account sitting within us.

00:15:53.496 --> 00:16:01.208
Every human has a place for Shri Ganesha and it is near the prostate gland, we call it MOOLADHAR chakra.

00:16:01.208 --> 00:16:08.840
establishment of Shri Ganesha . The triangular bone is called Mooladhar where mother Kundalini is sitting.

00:16:08.840 --> 00:16:20.175
Just under that triangular bone, Shri Ganesha is protecting her rather protecting her chastity.

00:16:20.175 --> 00:16:26.063
Now we know how Shri Gauri established Shri Ganesha.

00:16:26.063 --> 00:16:29.883
She was married but had not yet met with her husband.

00:16:29.883 --> 00:16:33.964
That time she had gone for her bath and after removing the dirt from her body……

00:16:33.964 --> 00:16:37.661
Now if you have vibrations in your entire – if your entire body has the divine vibrations

00:16:37.661 --> 00:16:43.365
and if this divine vibration is flowing and if that is taken in the dirt of one’s  body then that too has divine vibrations.

00:16:43.365 --> 00:16:51.994
She created Ganapati out of this dirt and kept it outside her bathing place.

00:16:51.994 --> 00:16:58.260
Now see, she kept him outside the bathing place  and not in the front from where the all the filth is flowing.

00:16:58.260 --> 00:17:06.981
Many of you must be knowing, when the water from the bathroom flows then many a times the leaves from patra(alu) or some people plant  lotus flowers also and they grow there quite well.

00:17:06.981 --> 00:17:12.471
It is quite surprising , the lotus flowers grow only where there is a puddle.

00:17:12.471 --> 00:17:15.648
Same is the example of Shri Ganesh.

00:17:15.648 --> 00:17:20.210
Means where  the dirtiest region  of the house is, on that dirty region of the house

00:17:20.210 --> 00:17:31.803
this lotus  has bloomed and with its perfume it imparts its fragrance to this dirt.

00:17:31.803 --> 00:17:38.638
This power of his also greatly helps us in our lives.

00:17:38.638 --> 00:17:44.970
The dirt that we see in us is   secured due to the Ganesh element.

00:17:44.970 --> 00:17:52.498
Now this Ganesh element has to first perform pujan(worship) of Kundalini means of Shri Gauri first.

00:17:52.498 --> 00:17:59.493
Means your Ganesh element first has to perform your Kundalini’s pujan.

00:17:59.493 --> 00:18:02.167
In short ,  to bring abodhita (innocence) in us .

00:18:02.167 --> 00:18:15.572
You will be surprised when Kundalini gets awakened that time the fragrance of the Ganesh element spreads in the entire body. (Mataji speaking – These are realized should, please sit here..It does not matter)

00:18:15.572 --> 00:18:35.554
Many people especially Sahaja Yogis sense the fragrance when Kundalini gets awakened.

00:18:35.554 --> 00:18:43.895
Because Ganesh element is made out of earth element or the earth itself is made out of Ganesh element.

00:18:43.895 --> 00:18:48.164
This earth is made out of Shri Maha     Ganesh(Ganesh Almighty).

00:18:48.164 --> 00:18:51.400
So the presence  of Shri  Ganesh in us, that too is comprised of the earth element.

00:18:51.400 --> 00:18:54.746
Now we know that all fragrances emanate out of   earth.

00:18:54.746 --> 00:18:56.770
The fragrances of all flowers emanate out of earth.

00:18:56.770 --> 00:19:00.693
That is why when Kundalini gets awakened many people sense different types of aromas.

00:19:00.693 --> 00:19:07.065
Not only this, many Sahaja Yogis tell me that Shri Mataji when we remember you we sense very intense fragrance and such fragrances emanate from your body also.

00:19:07.065 --> 00:19:14.445
Many people misunderstand that Shri Mataji wears some perfume but it is not so.

00:19:14.445 --> 00:19:18.398
If the Ganesh element is awakened in you then the fragrance emanates from within.

00:19:18.398 --> 00:19:20.322
Different types of fragrances emanate out of a person.

00:19:20.322 --> 00:19:27.158
But you must be knowing that there are such people in world  who call themselves as Sadhus or saints and they cannot  live with fragrance.

00:19:27.158 --> 00:19:30.024
They call themselves God and they cannot tolerate fragrance.

00:19:30.024 --> 00:19:33.397
We have explicit writings on this.

00:19:33.397 --> 00:19:40.101
You read any deity’s description. Especially that of Shri Ganesha. That He loves fragrance.

00:19:40.101 --> 00:19:43.590
Not only that, He loves flowers.

00:19:43.590 --> 00:19:45.297
And He loves lotus.

00:19:45.297 --> 00:19:50.010
Similarly it is written in the description of  Shri Vishnu, written in the description of the Goddesses.

00:19:50.010 --> 00:19:58.582
This means that those people who do not like fragrance ,  who cannot tolerate fragrance they have some serious flaw and they are against the God Almighty.

00:19:58.582 --> 00:20:01.742
They do not have the power of the Almighty for sure.

00:20:01.742 --> 00:20:06.122
The person who cannot tolerate fragrance at all, he certainly has some anti-God  elements in him.

00:20:06.122 --> 00:20:11.863
Because fragrance is a great principle of the Earth element.

00:20:11.863 --> 00:20:17.626
There are many names for it in the language of Yoga.

00:20:17.626 --> 00:20:21.621
Its no use telling about it that as you would keep thinking about it.

00:20:21.621 --> 00:20:32.447
But the important point to note is, whatever five significant elements are and before that whatever life elements they have , the first  amongst  these is the element of fragrance.

00:20:32.447 --> 00:20:39.303
This element constitutes the earth.  Shri Ganesh is made up of this life element.

00:20:39.303 --> 00:20:49.859
Therefore before worshipping Lord Ganesha , one must exude  perfume  ourselves that means our lives should have a subtle fragrance.

00:20:49.859 --> 00:21:00.267
Not at an overt level. A person who  is very wicked, is very vile at an overt level, has an equally fowl smell.

00:21:00.267 --> 00:21:03.318
Such a person from Sahaja Yoga’s perspective is fowl smelling…

00:21:03.318 --> 00:21:06.706
On the outside  even if the person smells good, still that person is not considered fragrant.

00:21:06.706 --> 00:21:09.289
Fragrance should be such that it should attract the person.

00:21:09.289 --> 00:21:18.051
