00:54:28.463 --> 00:54:31.715
And even if you want divinity you have to be in this world.

00:54:31.715 --> 00:54:38.440
If you stick to intense and difficult renunciation you may get the title of ‘Brahmarshi’.

00:54:38.440 --> 00:54:41.243
