00:54:41.243 --> 00:54:45.435
I know a lot of them but they are not prepared to do anything now.

00:54:45.435 --> 00:54:50.141
They do not have the earnest desire and they are not ready to take so much effort.

00:54:50.141 --> 00:54:56.416
I sometimes feel sad,their opinion is that whosoever are their devotees – they are not yet ready.

00:54:56.416 --> 00:55:00.325
If we are ready to take effort then we can prepare them and get them ahead.

00:55:00.325 --> 00:55:05.968
Quite a few times I feel that it will be good if all these people come forward and helped me.They revere me a lot.

00:55:05.968 --> 00:55:14.567
There is a gentleman near Calcutta who is an accomplished person

00:55:14.567 --> 00:55:23.081
and he told an American about me,’ Now that Mataji has arrived, we are observing her work.

00:55:23.081 --> 00:55:24.193
