00:55:24.193 --> 00:55:29.910
We also want to do this work and destroying the demons etc.- that we are accomplishing by our mental prowess.‘

00:55:29.910 --> 00:55:32.719
But when I asked the American,’why don’t you take him to America?’

00:55:32.719 --> 00:55:35.533
He went to America and came back in 5 days flat

00:55:35.533 --> 00:55:38.781
and said to me,’ I do not wish to meet such people.They are very dirty people.‘

00:55:38.781 --> 00:55:41.649
This is because he is not used to people yet.

00:55:41.649 --> 00:55:45.480
One could say- He cannot tolerate too many people around him as he has been staying away from people.

00:55:45.480 --> 00:55:49.658
Now what happened due to this is that if you come across a saint or a hermit,

00:55:49.658 --> 00:55:57.613
you would fall at his feet,you would bestow your faith in him–due to this you will no doubt improve your state but how will you attain self realization?

00:55:57.613 --> 00:55:59.285
Because to achieve that you need to put your hands in the filth.

00:55:59.285 --> 00:56:01.663
If you wish to improve your child, need to bring up your child

00:56:01.663 --> 00:56:03.602
the mother has to deal with filth.

00:56:03.602 --> 00:56:05.936
If she hates the filth then who will clean the child?

00:56:05.936 --> 00:56:08.486
And hence it is the work of a mother only.

00:56:08.486 --> 00:56:10.800
And I am doing the work of a Mother in Sahaja Yoga.

00:56:10.800 --> 00:56:19.072
You all can bathe in it, take pleasure out of it – this is the desire of a Mother.

00:56:19.072 --> 00:56:23.488
The only wish a mother has is that whatever power she has One may be divine or whatever – you can be so in your own home.

00:56:23.488 --> 00:56:28.358
What is your use to us?You may be  so called Bhagwan etc. what is his use to us ?

00:56:28.358 --> 00:56:33.262
Until the common folks benefit from it,until the common folks can get something

00:56:33.262 --> 00:56:37.545
out of him until their children get their powers–what is the use of such a mother?

00:56:37.545 --> 00:56:40.080
It is better not to be such a mother than to be one.

00:56:40.080 --> 00:56:51.491
So the person whom you consider to be a guru or your mother, consider elder to yourself, if he has not understood himself then what ideal can you derive from him?

00:56:51.491 --> 00:56:57.965
In Sahaja Yoga you can derive the meaning of ‘Swa”.Meaning of Swa’-  means you can relate to the relevance of your atma.

00:56:57.965 --> 00:56:59.661
This I would explain to you in my next lecture.

00:56:59.661 --> 00:57:01.301
At the moment I have explained about the Ganesh element.

00:57:01.301 --> 00:57:08.550
