00:57:23.595 --> 00:57:26.677
And you must get all that knowledge and you WILL get it

00:57:26.677 --> 00:57:28.806
and I will not hide anything about it.

00:57:28.806 --> 00:57:31.310
I am ready to explain everything to you.

00:57:31.310 --> 00:57:35.790
but you will have to put all the efforts after realization.

00:57:35.790 --> 00:57:38.669
If you don’t work hard you won’t get any benefit.

00:57:38.669 --> 00:57:45.708
Now today’s program is about awakening the Kundalini.I think you should work hard for this.

00:57:45.708 --> 00:57:49.123
Now people have a query as to what should be done in the pooja.‘

00:57:49.123 --> 00:57:51.298
‘Shri Mataji, what should be done on the occasion of Shri Ganesha pooja?‘

00:57:51.298 --> 00:58:01.337
I have the knowledge beyond the obvious that you cannot see, what Nanak has called as ‘ALAKH” ( which cannot be seen or perceived).

00:58:01.337 --> 00:58:06.227
I see with those eyes.So first of all I want to tell you to examine if you are chaste enough.

00:58:06.227 --> 00:58:11.033
To take bath etc. is all ok.Even if you don’t do that it is alright.

