00:58:29.196 --> 00:58:33.404
Means in Sahaja Yoga,Hindus, Muslims, Christians, all are included.

00:58:33.404 --> 00:58:36.023
And moreover it has been shown how their deities are included in Sahaja Yoga.

00:58:36.023 --> 00:58:41.323
This Ganesh element, when it comes on the Agnya chakra, it took the form of Christ when it came in this world.

00:58:41.323 --> 00:58:47.417
You would have read in ‘Devi Mahatmya’, the Bhagwat written by Shri Markandeya.

00:58:47.417 --> 00:58:52.052
you could say Markandeya is my most beloved son.

00:58:52.052 --> 00:58:57.242
Nowadays nobody reads Markandeya, but if you can get it, read the description of Shri Maha Vishnu.

00:58:57.242 --> 00:59:00.276
