00:59:11.632 --> 00:59:14.948
Now Christ.Since Radha had created him, he is called Christ in the name of Krishna

00:59:14.948 --> 00:59:18.778
and since Yashoda is there, hence Yeshu.

00:59:18.778 --> 00:59:28.599
In this way he has positioned  the Ganesh element in the form of Christ.

00:59:28.599 --> 00:59:34.248
