that this may be due to something else, that may have a different cause.

01:00:38.969 --> 01:00:43.967
This means you have not reached at your inference, your connection has not yet been established, so get it established.

01:00:43.967 --> 01:00:46.271
First of all,get your self realization. That is what I want to tell.

